---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SiteHeader from '../components/SiteHeader.astro';
import SiteFooter from '../components/SiteFooter.astro';

const CONTACT_EMAIL = 'hello@unnatural.info';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="About UNNATURAL: a working draft of a theory of everything, the method behind it, and how to reach the author."
>
  <SiteHeader />
  <main class="ab">
    <div class="ab__container">

      <header class="ab__header">
        <p class="ab__kicker">
          <span class="ab__kicker-glyph" aria-hidden="true">§</span>
          About this work
        </p>
        <h1 class="ab__title">A working draft, in the open.</h1>
        <p class="ab__lead">
          UNNATURAL is a book written in public. The chapters are drafts. The framing shifts week to week. Nothing here is a final claim.
        </p>
      </header>

      <section class="ab__section">
        <h2 class="ab__heading">What it is</h2>
        <div class="ab__prose">
          <p>
            One working answer to the child's question <em>what are we?</em> It argues that we are natural beings who slipped into the information realm and now loop it back through the physical world that made us.
          </p>
          <p>
            The argument runs in three movements. Act&nbsp;I locates the floor of life in wanting, not thinking. Act&nbsp;II (<code>init.d</code>) argues that a finite observer cannot meet a fractal, chaotic universe whole, so distinction is how living things boot up inside the excess. Act&nbsp;III names the growth loop (Measure, Model, Manifest) and traces it from a single cell to a civilisation.
          </p>
          <p>
            The site is the working surface. The <a href="/wiki/">wiki</a> is the compiled residue.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="ab__section">
        <h2 class="ab__heading">Who</h2>
        <div class="ab__prose">
          <p>
            Written by Sahil Dawka. More at <a href="https://sahil.pro" rel="noopener">sahil.pro</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="ab__section">
        <h2 class="ab__heading">Method</h2>
        <div class="ab__prose">
          <p>
            The frame is <em>unscientific empirical</em>. Unscientific because it refuses to wait for lab equipment to catch up before talking about will, distinction, meaning, or growth. Empirical because every claim is meant to be checkable against a reader's own life, and revisable when it is not.
          </p>
          <p>
            Three commitments run through every chapter. Mark what we observe. Mark what we interpret. Mark what we don't yet know.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="ab__section">
        <h2 class="ab__heading">Colophon</h2>
        <dl class="ab__colophon">
          <div class="ab__colophon-row">
            <dt>Display</dt>
            <dd><em>Fraunces</em>, variable optical size and SOFT axes.</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="ab__colophon-row">
            <dt>Body</dt>
            <dd><em>Source Serif 4</em>, tuned for screen reading.</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="ab__colophon-row">
            <dt>Technical</dt>
            <dd><em>JetBrains Mono</em>, for chapter numbers, labels, and the <code>init.d</code> reference.</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="ab__colophon-row">
            <dt>Built with</dt>
            <dd>Astro and plain CSS. The paper grain is an inlined SVG. Dark mode follows your system.</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="ab__colophon-row">
            <dt>Source</dt>
            <dd><a href="https://github.com/sdawka/unnatural-info" rel="noopener">github.com/sdawka/unnatural-info</a></dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </section>

      <section class="ab__section ab__section--contact">
        <h2 class="ab__heading">Contact</h2>
        <div class="ab__prose">
          <p>
            Notes, objections, corrections, and questions are all welcome. This is a working draft, and the argument gets sharper when it meets resistance.
          </p>
          <a class="ab__email" href={`mailto:${CONTACT_EMAIL}?subject=Unnatural`}>
            <span class="ab__email-label">Write</span>
            <span class="ab__email-addr">{CONTACT_EMAIL}</span>
            <span class="ab__email-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

    </div>
  </main>
  <SiteFooter />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .ab {
    padding: var(--space-16) var(--safe-right) var(--space-16) var(--safe-left);
  }

  .ab__container {
    max-width: var(--page-max);
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-12);
  }

  .ab__header {
    max-width: 48rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-6);
    border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--color-rule);
  }

  .ab__kicker {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    color: var(--color-ink-muted);
  }

  .ab__kicker-glyph {
    font-size: 1.2em;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--color-ink-faint);
  }

  .ab__title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 96, 'wght' 340, 'SOFT' 60;
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    line-height: 1.02;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  @media (min-width: 48rem) {
    .ab__title { font-size: var(--text-5xl); }
  }

  .ab__lead {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 30, 'wght' 360, 'SOFT' 40;
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--color-ink-muted);
    max-width: 52ch;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-top: var(--space-2);
  }

  .ab__section {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-8);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-rule-soft);
  }

  .ab__section:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  @media (min-width: 54rem) {
    .ab__section {
      grid-template-columns: 14rem 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-8);
    }
  }

  .ab__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    color: var(--color-ink-muted);
    font-weight: 400;
    padding-top: 0.4em;
  }

  .ab__prose {
    max-width: 60ch;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: var(--lh-body);
    color: var(--color-ink);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  .ab__prose em {
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .ab__prose a {
    color: inherit;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-rule);
    transition: border-color var(--dur-fast), color var(--dur-fast);
  }

  .ab__prose a:hover {
    border-bottom-color: var(--color-ink);
  }

  .ab__prose code {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.9em;
    background-color: var(--color-ground-tint);
    padding: 0.05em 0.35em;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  /* Colophon */
  .ab__colophon {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    max-width: 60ch;
  }

  .ab__colophon-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 7rem 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-2);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-rule-soft);
  }

  .ab__colophon-row:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .ab__colophon dt {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--color-ink-muted);
    padding-top: 0.3em;
  }

  .ab__colophon dd {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-ink);
    line-height: 1.45;
  }

  .ab__colophon em {
    font-style: italic;
    font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 16, 'wght' 500;
  }

  @media (max-width: 36rem) {
    .ab__colophon-row {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-1);
    }
    .ab__colophon dt { padding-top: 0; }
  }

  /* Contact button */
  .ab__email {
    display: inline-grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto auto auto;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    padding: var(--space-4) var(--space-5);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-rule);
    text-decoration: none !important;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    transition: border-color var(--dur-med) var(--ease-out), background-color var(--dur-med) var(--ease-out);
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-ground-tint) 30%, transparent);
    align-self: flex-start;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-rule) !important;
  }

  .ab__email:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-ink);
    background: var(--color-ground-tint);
  }

  .ab__email-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    color: var(--color-ink-muted);
  }

  .ab__email-addr {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-ink);
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }

  .ab__email-arrow {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--color-ink-muted);
    transition: transform var(--dur-med) var(--ease-out), color var(--dur-fast);
  }

  .ab__email:hover .ab__email-arrow {
    color: var(--color-ink);
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }
</style>
